headline: What Your Home's Architecture Says About Price, Popularity and Place: Realtor.com速 Unveils 2025 Style Trends
summary: A new analysis from Realtor.com速 reveals how architectural style can reflect everything from your home's price to its location, size and age. Drawing on thousands of single-family listings from May 2025, the report dives into six key architectural categories to spotlight the most common, and most costly, styles across the country.
